    "d5_testimonial_rnjgbA": {
      "type": "d5-testimonial",
      "blocks": {
        "review_7XNFCG": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "img": "shopify://shop_images/k_ij_b.webp",
            "heading": "",
            "rt": "<p>I just got the fleece hoodie and matching sweatpants, and I am obsessed! The fabric is unbelievably soft—it truly feels like I’m wrapped in a cloud of pure coziness. The fit is perfect—just keep in mind that it’s designed to have a relaxed, oversized fit.</p>",
            "name": "<p><em><strong>Julie Wren</strong></em></p>"
          }
        },
        "review_NXYwcD": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "img": "shopify://shop_images/j.webp",
            "heading": "",
            "rt": "<p>Absolutely happy with the hoodie. I ordered white in a size Large. I’m 5’11 and it is a bit oversized but I like it , super cozy. I def wore it to the bay area!! New obsession.</p>",
            "name": "<p><em><strong>Windsor Grey</strong></em></p>"
          }
        },
        "review_CtQVLK": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "img": "shopify://shop_images/output-0f5b1cbd-3c26-425b-a393-2370f8e36105-0.webp",
            "heading": "",
            "rt": "<p>I am obsessed with the quality of this set! Our manager surprised us with a hoodie and sweatpants from the fleece company. it’s beyond comfortable & i don’t want to take it off! Now it has become a dress code for us. I definitely won’t shut up about how awesome it is!</p>",
            "name": "<p><em><strong>Melina Rodriguez</strong></em></p>"
          }
        },
        "review_XVyzi4": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "img": "shopify://shop_images/output-94e46aec-4b9d-41a4-b315-ad89593572dc-1_1.webp",
            "heading": "",
            "rt": "<p>This sweatsuit have made such a deep Impact on my sleep life! I have never, ever, ever slept in a sweatshirt. I have hot flashes and I get really hot! But I am able to sleep in this one! I also got the matching blanket and pillows. My bedroom literally looks and feels like clouds rn. Thanks so much!</p>",
            "name": "<p><em><strong>Andrea Fisherman</strong></em></p>"
          }
        },
        "review_K3hJUt": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "img": "shopify://shop_images/ijb.webp",
            "heading": "",
            "rt": "<p>Not only was there fast shipping, but the items came in great condition. The colors were even better than I imagined, the quality is superb. The sweatsuits are so soft and I’m extremely impressed with the comfort! I’ll be buying again asap!</p>",
            "name": "<p><em><strong>Henry Longford</strong></em></p>"
          }
        },
        "review_JY6qaD": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "img": "shopify://shop_images/7B058847-39C8-433A-B612-C08C5C049796.webp",
            "heading": "",
            "rt": "<p>(Studio Photo) I absolutely love this brand! Such good quality, so soft! I wear them everywhere just got my 3rd or 4th set, their full dark grey combo set!!</p>",
            "name": "<p><em><strong>Kelly Karmen</strong></em></p>"
          }
        },
        "review_GpmH7H": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "img": "shopify://shop_images/output-2_26_1.webp",
            "heading": "",
            "rt": "<p>Love Love Love my fleece hoodie! They’re my go to when it’s freezing cold outside because I can be comfortable and still be warm and cute at the same time!!</p>",
            "name": "<p><em><strong>Amy Steinfeld</strong></em></p>"
          }
        },
        "review_WpD789": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "img": "shopify://shop_images/output-0_10_7d063d94-e45c-4eff-a77a-3101271dda79.webp",
            "heading": "",
            "rt": "<p>(Studio Photo) Literally the best set ever!! My girlfriend got the coziest hoodie & sweats for me and it literally feels like a cloud and actually is amazing quality.</p>",
            "name": "<p><em><strong>Nick Taylor</strong></em></p>"
          }
        },
        "review_WwR648": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "img": "shopify://shop_images/output-1_27_1.webp",
            "heading": "",
            "rt": "<p>(Professional Photo) I received this for my bday and man, i really like it . I got the dark grey one and it’s perfect. Have been wearing them everywhere.</p>",
            "name": "<p><em><strong>Dylan Derubeis</strong></em></p>"
          }
        },
        "review_RwLgrk": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "img": "shopify://shop_images/fixed-image-0_51_1.webp",
            "heading": "",
            "rt": "<p>(Studio Photo) i absolutely loveeee these sweats! so comfortable & they really do keep you warm! i live in New York & girl does it get so cold out here!! These are a lifesaver, thanks xoxo!!!!</p>",
            "name": "<p><em><strong>Shirley Rivilla</strong></em></p>"
          }
        },
        "review_CQkrcb": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "",
            "rt": "<p>Came so fast, I tried it on to see how it fit and didn’t take it off the rest of the day 😂 This is ACTUALLY comforting!</p>",
            "name": "<p><em><strong>Melizza De Leon</strong></em></p>"
          }
        },
        "review_rrmkBX": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "",
            "rt": "<p>I’m a Boston girl, and the harsh winters here can be overwhelming, but I’ve found that having comfortable clothing really helps alleviate seasonal depression. This is perfect for lounging around the house or running errands, and I always get compliments on them!</p>",
            "name": "<p><em><strong>Kelly Peterson</strong></em></p>"
          }
        },
        "review_nqzG3Q": {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "",
            "rt": "<p>The team is very quick to respond to messages and questions. The products are of the utmost quality and comfort!</p>",
            "name": "<p><em><strong>Lisa Prosser</strong></em></p>"
          }
        }
      },
